					<![CDATA[
						 <p>1) I think the containment procedures section should say something about -1 holding cells being monitored via CC TV, since otherwise they'd be unobserved and disappear.</p> <p>2) The containment procedures section could mention monitoring psych wards and the Internet for descriptions of stage 1 and stage 2, and then going out and securing affected people.</p> <p>3) So I guess that Foundation personnel have been unable to communicate to the -1s?</p> <p>4) I guess the -1s in containment cells just stop communicating, rather than writing out &quot;Let me go&quot; or &quot;Why can't I reach him&quot;?</p> 
				 	]]>
